Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得找到基拉·汀斯利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要么跟血腥約翰是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么馬上就要成為他下一個目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰干的  告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  她說什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說血腥約翰左肩膀有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馬里布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,500)\fs18\pos(193.8,204.8)}加利福尼亞  馬里布  簡的家宅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-簡  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別這么做  別扔下我這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  求你了  你身處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣做是在自尋死路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(189,132)}兩天前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,132)\fad(0,400)}星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紋身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以用那個來確定血腥約翰的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們只要一個個檢查疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看哪個人身上就紋身就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰還不知道我發現紋身的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果我們去查他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能血腥約翰會發現此事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在我們還沒機會接近他的時候就銷聲匿跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們打算怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把五名疑犯同時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合到一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再檢查是否有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就直接叫他們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得他們會同意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒打算給他們選擇的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成行了  還有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊特·斯特爾斯因兩起謀殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被聯調局通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  二十多年前的懸案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都過去那么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局現在才跟進嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們肯定是有了什么新的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法醫證據  目擊證人  -那斯特爾斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關鍵就是這個  沒人知道他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連聯調局也不知道  斯特爾斯幾周前就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  但我們會找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我配合你的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你揭露血腥約翰身份的時候我要在場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我說了好的  -說是說了  但你說的肯定不算數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事沒有商量的余地  簡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我百分百同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為我之前說得夠清楚了  探員們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不知道布萊特·斯特爾斯在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我們也表達得很清楚了  你這說法我們不買賬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯把天眼組織的領導權留給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他卻沒有告訴你他躲藏在哪里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根本說不通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯自始至終
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都將教徒的需要放在他自己之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想讓我知道是因為他想保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因為他不想被人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不覺得布萊特·斯特爾斯擔心是否會被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起來很有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯在我們這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實世界里的時間  是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我們說話的這會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在做好心理和身體上的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以擺脫我們這個物質世界的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是非常天真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常無知的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊特·斯特爾斯不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要將自己提升到一個新的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這種道行不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要非常艱難才能觸碰到這種高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然我們中有人對此是無法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡  加了一份奶油  一份糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了  拉塞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要準備好了的話鑒證小組就要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我查明他的身份  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我怕高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  有人來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰的案子有了重大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了一些新線索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常重要的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  現在還不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道能信任誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道能不能信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰有一些位高權重的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但不能在這說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八點見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四  為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要時間找一個安全的見面地點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  在哪見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到了那天再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經犯過很多次錯誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是低估了血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再犯這種錯誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想知道線索  就要聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是麥卡利斯特警長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警長嗎  我是派翠克·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克  最近怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我打電話是有事想問你  -問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上個月我去納帕谷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說聽任我的調遣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說話算數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我是講信用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我能指望你幫我個忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八點我需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到那天我再告訴你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是關于血腥約翰的事  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們準備好了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  伊夫林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  這是給您的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}派翠克·簡正在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚你們在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將見證我升天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這個世界  飛升到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個世外的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要為我哀悼  我的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這并非逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說  唐  你養的不是一個情婦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是一個想要報復你  會毀掉你的瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你走運  我的工作就是解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在要做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要給她開張支票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給她很大一筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后祈禱這事就這么完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果還沒完  也別擔心  唐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多種辦法可以讓一個女人閉嘴  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高興見到你  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  請給我來一杯黑咖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上八點把我叫來干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個調查需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  如果你找我幫忙那這就很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  特蕾莎  我還不了解你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和簡對血腥約翰的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有進展了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"也許"  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么要搞得這么神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說真的  為什么要瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們該不會覺得我是血腥約翰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是這么想的  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要想找我問話  那就逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則就別把我扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果問不管用  我不問了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不為加調局工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在無法得到執法人員所能得到的保護了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么  你威脅我  -不是我  是簡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明天晚上想見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不去  他就會認為你是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他會找你麻煩的  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你了解簡的  你知道他身上發生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道血腥約翰對他做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我  我不會拿這個試探他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不怕派翠克·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去和他見一面又有什么關系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果去了  你和簡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會再懷疑我是血腥約翰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后絕對不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒說完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是在折磨我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特爾斯  -他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在哪兒  -我幫不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都為天眼組織工作這么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想抓他  我只想跟他談談
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幫我這個忙  算我欠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在在做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲早你會需要我幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷·哈弗內說斯特爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架私人飛機供其往來國內不被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機主是一個名叫萊恩·帕克斯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕克斯  知道了  我去查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡到局里了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  沒見他的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(189.6,266.4)}加州  帕羅奧多  帕羅奧多機場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉莫特先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  有什么可效勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周探員  瑞斯比探員  加調局的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想請你回答幾個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚有一架G6私人飛機降落在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注冊尾號為M550MT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大約十一點左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道飛機上的人是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  私人飛機不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供乘客名單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有碰巧見到有誰從飛機上下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  有汽車服務公司的人來接他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可能幫得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會正好知道那個汽車服務公司的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽車服務公司那邊怎么說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說昨晚從機場接到了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操著英國口音的銀發男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-斯特爾斯  -我們也是這么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地址是厄瓜多爾領事館
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舊金山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好樣的  你們倆去查查看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  范佩爾  不如你一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們能利用這個優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒有  -沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我沒問題的  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-職責所在  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就干點跑腿的活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了  有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈弗內答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  斯特爾斯那邊怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾好像瞄準他的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就還剩一個血腥約翰案疑犯要約談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正往他辦公室走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-咱們那邊見嗎  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(190.8,267.2)}加利福尼亞  舊金山  厄瓜多爾領事館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯·范佩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次見到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次有何貴干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是簡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要你幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差你來  他可真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我到底能為派翠克·簡做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想見見你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天晚上八點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我們上次一別  你變樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟我說你嫁給那個只會傻笑的呆子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你會去見簡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能見他我再高興不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很樂意  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸的是  鑒于我現在的境況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不太能成行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說因為聯邦調查局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你功課做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不知道我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他們也就不知道你在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要是不肯見簡  他們就會知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的確變了  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去過厄瓜多爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很多很多年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那傳教來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的人很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有個年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很窮  但野心勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在他身上看到了些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我決定試著幫幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫他付學費
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實也沒什么  但你猜怎么著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么多年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子已經是國務部長了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很為他高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他邀請我住在這豪華的領事館里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這一片小小的外國領土上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外國領土  如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不受你們加調局  聯調局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與任何美國法律管轄的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  格蕾斯  你的威脅不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  很高興能再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我跟簡問個好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去的時候隨手關門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啊  我感覺輕松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官  案子有突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么案子  -血腥約翰案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上就能確定兇手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的確定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你們有了切實答案要立刻告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此案結束的時候我要在場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等您這句話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛和派翠克·簡談了點有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖那邊怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上鉤了  斯特爾斯那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不太好  -你找到他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還有什么問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在厄瓜多爾領事館里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他在里面  我們就動不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來對付斯特爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會也不必跟你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我的說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霰彈槍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火力夠大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關于明天晚上的事  我們得談談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先聽我說完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不希望我在場是因為你覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會阻止你殺血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是你不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像血腥約翰這種禽獸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本連上庭受審的資格都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種人就該就地正法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  讓我搞搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在執法部門干了快二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然就這么改變原則了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在血腥約翰案上嗎  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很驚訝  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  你不相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我認識的最誠實的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情上  你絕不會騙我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明晚見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\pos(192,131)\fad(0,400)}星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  我親愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近來還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  那么說你不是來找我聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明晚八點你要來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-派翠克  -不  你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你明晚八點來見我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則等到我再回來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這是領事館也保不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是你的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說的話句句當真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將死之人還怕什么死亡威脅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝模作樣騙騙你那些信徒還行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.31,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.68,0:24:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.94,0:24:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不是裝的了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.16,0:24:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還剩多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.77,0:24:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經擴散到血液了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.12,0:24:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無藥可醫了  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.69,0:24:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許兩周  也許一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.23,0:24:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是針對你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:24:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.78,0:25:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間對我來說太寶貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.39,0:25:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我還是需要你來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事如此重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.34,0:25:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.00,0:25:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終于接近他了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未有的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.03,0:25:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.29,0:25:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我若能去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.21,0:25:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是再高興不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.32,0:25:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的情況比你想象的復雜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.18,0:25:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困在這兒還有別的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.24,0:25:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  事實正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.08,0:25:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們跟我到這里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.80,0:25:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等著我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.52,0:25:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我想呆在這兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.51,0:25:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.75,0:25:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么說聯調局是唯一的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.15,0:25:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意  前門有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.23,0:26:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天眼組織的車
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.63,0:26:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在偷偷往外轉移什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.78,0:26:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時準備行動
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.84,0:26:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即行動  行動  上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不許動  -不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.35,0:26:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在方向盤上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.71,0:26:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在我們能看見的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.66,0:26:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好  先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.39,0:26:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么能為你們效勞的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.83,0:27:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯入局了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.69,0:27:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.64,0:27:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可有很長一段車程
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}晚上八點  馬里布  雪松街1309號見  走便道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.42,0:27:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}信息已發送
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.02,0:27:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么薩城警局只有等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.78,0:27:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想用職權壓人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.52,0:27:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有必要我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱文  回頭我再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.69,0:28:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.23,0:28:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看日落
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.20,0:29:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本  有些話我想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.22,0:29:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很早以前就應該跟你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.51,0:29:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚點再謝也不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.67,0:29:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.31,0:29:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須現在就說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.20,0:29:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.81,0:29:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你對我意味著什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.51,0:29:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.73,0:30:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.19,0:30:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點忘了  我有個驚喜給你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.73,0:30:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這等我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.31,0:30:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.08,0:30:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.35,0:31:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馬里布
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.65,0:31:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(300,300)\fs18\pos(191.4,268)}加利福尼亞  馬里布  簡的家宅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.10,0:34:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請停車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.32,0:34:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.48,0:34:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州調查局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.83,0:34:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我要征用你的車
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.13,0:34:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.19,0:34:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.03,0:34:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即下車  快
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.15,0:34:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.80,0:34:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.51,0:34:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要報警
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.88,0:34:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.58,0:35:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-簡  -喂  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.64,0:35:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  別這么做  別扔下我這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.23,0:35:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.60,0:35:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  求你了  你身處險境
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.27,0:35:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.40,0:35:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.18,0:35:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.11,0:35:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣做是在自尋死路
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.27,0:35:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.21,0:35:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.56,0:35:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.69,0:36:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.67,0:37:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來早了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.06,0:37:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不早  來得正好  坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,911  您遇到了什么緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.48,0:37:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是加州調查局的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.85,0:37:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎·里斯本探員
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.65,0:37:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請派警員到馬里布的雪松街1309號
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.69,0:37:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有探員需要立即支援
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓你們五個聚在一起是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.55,0:37:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.87,0:37:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人可能猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.88,0:37:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們中的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.27,0:37:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.96,0:37:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  在我們幾個中間
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.57,0:37:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們其中之一是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.55,0:37:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.02,0:37:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是誰  -我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.08,0:38:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到這來就是為了找出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.27,0:38:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想說這個房間里的某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.39,0:38:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.56,0:38:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我很確定  -太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.96,0:38:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證完全不荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.16,0:38:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證  我才不跟你在這兒胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.43,0:38:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.25,0:38:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步都別想往門口走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.74,0:38:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不準走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.62,0:38:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放輕松  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.25,0:38:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起來很緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.33,0:38:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.57,0:38:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.38,0:38:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.97,0:38:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢把你們的槍拿出來  放在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.08,0:38:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推到我這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.18,0:38:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.71,0:38:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.11,0:39:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.32,0:39:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.71,0:39:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.54,0:39:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.52,0:39:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為這一刻  我等了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.80,0:39:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年來  血腥約翰一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.65,0:39:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們中的某個人一直很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.86,0:39:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很謹慎  除了這次
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.57,0:39:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一次  你露出馬腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.72,0:39:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我說了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.66,0:39:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告訴我殺她的人  也就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.10,0:39:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.02,0:39:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.71,0:39:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.77,0:39:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都得
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.41,0:39:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.48,0:39:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻動手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.99,0:39:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始脫吧  快
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.86,0:39:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.22,0:40:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.84,0:40:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.89,0:40:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想得那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.29,0:40:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你弄錯了  -住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.47,0:40:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.71,0:40:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.83,0:40:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.40,0:40:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.54,0:41:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.21,0:41:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到他們倆那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.10,0:41:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別動
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.23,0:41:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你們三個
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.40,0:41:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到墻邊站著  快
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.58,0:41:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馬里布
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.51,0:42:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
